-- American Realty says not in merger talks with NorthStar Realty
-- By Sagarika Jaisinghani in Bangalore
-- Tue Apr 29, 2014 06:04AM EDT
-- None



April 29 (Reuters) - American Realty Capital Properties Inc <ARCP.O> said it was not in merger talks with NorthStar Realty Finance Corp <NRF.N>.

"ARCP actively evaluates opportunities and is in discussions with many companies over potential combinations; however, the company is not currently in discussions with NorthStar," American Realty said in a statement on Tuesday. [ID:nPn7MNZ62] Sources told Reuters on Monday that American Realty was in talks to buy NorthStar Realty. [ID:nL3N0NK4J2]